    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222950/extras/44e8a33689ab6d678d38af30d11ca4f1.poster.avif?t=1750071999\" width=480 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222950/extras/44e8a33689ab6d678d38af30d11ca4f1.webm?t=1750071999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>两种风格迥异的模式，往返在现实和想象之间！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222950/extras/6683426347f3c14e13195ab4a60d6c08.poster.avif?t=1750071999\" width=620 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222950/extras/6683426347f3c14e13195ab4a60d6c08.webm?t=1750071999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>在探索部分，帮助Damien克服初次在日本生活的挑战，自由探索奶奶家，展开在现实世界的小冒险！<br>在战斗部分，通过“强力组合”和“协力组合”释放Jump+英雄伙伴的经典绝招，把敌人一网打尽！战斗结合益智和潜行元素，富有战略性，不同种类的技能可以产生巨大伤害或造成大范围攻击，各种效果和玩法任您选择！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222950/extras/168375872e668a010a817bc3753f78ac.poster.avif?t=1750071999\" width=620 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222950/extras/168375872e668a010a817bc3753f78ac.webm?t=1750071999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222950/extras/4739401eae6f34f4fcc22466342b4efd.poster.avif?t=1750071999\" width=620 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222950/extras/4739401eae6f34f4fcc22466342b4efd.webm?t=1750071999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222950/extras/a1a03743385853497178a34d515308fc.poster.avif?t=1750071999\" width=620 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222950/extras/a1a03743385853497178a34d515308fc.webm?t=1750071999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222950/extras/b46452a01eb8ae690100f3285fb571d1.poster.avif?t=1750071999\" width=480 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222950/extras/b46452a01eb8ae690100f3285fb571d1.webm?t=1750071999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222950/extras/897574f82fdd1b87b77b0bdd3e6c9650.avif?t=1750071999\" width=500 height=396 /></span><br>Damien是一名性格内向的少年。他搬到日本后，想象中创造了一个“Captain Velvet Meteor”的英雄。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222950/extras/f1aae8c0cecce2f50a4c9dcb73b51ea6.avif?t=1750071999\" width=500 height=396 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222950/extras/9465515507a34f79d80ae1f7c1eba44f.poster.avif?t=1750071999\" width=620 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222950/extras/9465515507a34f79d80ae1f7c1eba44f.webm?t=1750071999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <br>于是他开始在想象世界里，与喜爱的Jump+英雄共赴冒险！Damien是否能克服困难，取回心灵的平静？<br> <br> <br>无论是男女老少、还是新手大佬，这款战略冒险游戏必定让大家都能玩得开心！",
